#: front-page.php:26
msgid "Built for Hawaii"
msgstr "Kōṃṃan ñan Hawaii"

#: front-page.php:33
msgid "Civic Engagement Tools"
msgstr "Kein Kōjparok Kien"

#: front-page.php:33
msgid "for the People of Hawaii"
msgstr "ñan Ri-Hawaii ro"

#: front-page.php:43
msgid "Government information shouldn't require a law degree to navigate. Civi.Me makes it simple to stay informed, show up, and have your voice heard — in plain language, for free."
msgstr "Melele in kien ekwe ejjeļọk an kōjjela lo ilo ilo bōk tiotio in lōñ ñan jeramman. Civi.Me elukkuun aenōmman bwe kwōnaaj jeļā, itok, im roñ am bōd — ilo kajin maroñ, jab tōprak."

#: front-page.php:53
msgid "What matters to you?"
msgstr "Etke ko remōj ñan eok?"

#: front-page.php:56
msgid "Browse meetings"
msgstr "Lale miting ko"

#: front-page.php:167
msgid "The challenge"
msgstr "Buñbūñ eo"

#: front-page.php:169
msgid "Civic participation should be accessible for all residents"
msgstr "Ekwe em̧ōj ñan armej ro otemjej bwe ren etal ilo kōjparok kien"

#: front-page.php:172
msgid "People want to be engaged, but the barriers make it feel impossible. We're removing them."
msgstr "Armej ro rej kōnan bōk oktak, ak kōt ko rej kōmmane bwe elōñ wōt bwe jeban maroñ. Kiiō jej kūr er."

#: front-page.php:190
msgid "Buried information"
msgstr "Melele ko rekōtoọn"

#: front-page.php:191
msgid "Meeting agendas are buried in PDFs across dozens of county and state websites with no consistent format."
msgstr "Agenda in miting ko rekōtoọn ilo PDF ko ilo website ko an kaltin im steit ko bwe ejjeļọk format ko rejjela."

#: front-page.php:203
msgid "No timely alerts"
msgstr "Ejjeļọk notification ko in mantin"

#: front-page.php:204
msgid "Residents find out about decisions that affect their neighborhoods after the fact — if at all."
msgstr "Ri-jikin ro rej jeļā kōn keemem ko rekōñjōñōt ñan aelon̄ ko aer jen ãlikin — bōlen aer jeļā ke."

#: front-page.php:219
msgid "Bureaucratic language"
msgstr "Kajin kien pālle"

#: front-page.php:220
msgid "Government documents are written for lawyers, not residents. Plain-language summaries are rare."
msgstr "Pepa ko an kien rejjōtake ñan ri-lōñ, jab ri-jikin. Jiroñ ko ilo kajin maroñ elōñlọk eddọ."

#: front-page.php:234
msgid "Who are my representatives?"
msgstr "Wōn ri-jokwe ro rōm̧ōj ñan eok?"

#: front-page.php:235
msgid "Most residents can't name their city council member, let alone their neighborhood board chair."
msgstr "Elōñlọk ri-jikin ro rejjab maroñ kōnaat etan ri-kaunsel in jikin ko aer, bōlen etan jemedre in board eo an aelon̄ aer."

#: front-page.php:254
msgid "Start here"
msgstr "Jino ijin"

#: front-page.php:256
msgid "Tell us what matters to you"
msgstr "Lōmnak eok etke ko remōj ñan eok"

#: front-page.php:259
msgid "Pick the topics you care about — environment, housing, education, health — and we'll show you the government meetings and councils that handle those issues."
msgstr "Kotak topic ko kwōjjab lọmọọj — environment, jikin mour, edukeiñ, olomiej — im kiiō jen kōjjeļā eok miting ko an kien im kaunsel ko rej kōṃṃan kōn ia."

