#: front-page.php:365
msgid "Browse Meetings"
msgstr "Lale Miting Ko"

#: front-page.php:368
msgid "All public meetings — boards, commissions, and councils — in one calendar. Filter by topic, council, or date. AI-generated summaries explain what's on the agenda."
msgstr "Miting in jikin ko otemjej — board ko, komisin ko, im kaunsel ko — ilo juon kaelendar. Filter kōn topic, kaunsel, ak raan. Jiroñ ko an AI rej kōjjeļā etke ko ilo agenda."

#: front-page.php:405
msgid "Council Profiles"
msgstr "Wōpij in Kaunsel Ko"

#: front-page.php:408
msgid "Learn what each board and commission actually does — in plain language. See who sits on the board, upcoming meetings, open seats, and how to participate."
msgstr "Jeļā etke board im komisin ko otemjej rej kōṃṃan — ilo kajin maroñ. Lale wōn rej jijet ilo board, miting ko rekooñāl, jikin ko jet, im wāween bōk oktak."

#: front-page.php:445
msgid "Get Alerts"
msgstr "Bōk Notification Ko"

#: front-page.php:448
msgid "Subscribe to topics or specific councils. Get email alerts when meetings are scheduled — before it's too late to participate."
msgstr "Subscribe ñan topic ko ak kaunsel ko kiloñi. Bōk notification in email ke miting ko rej schedule — mokta jen jab maroñ bōk oktak."

#: front-page.php:489
msgid "Guides & Compliance"
msgstr "Guide ko im Mōkaj"

#: front-page.php:492
msgid "Step-by-step civic action guides plus compliance tools for agencies — Sunshine Law, public records, accessibility, and public participation best practices."
msgstr "Guide ko in kōjparok kien im kein mōkaj ñan ejmour ko — Sunshine Law, rekōd in jikin, maroñ bōk, im wāween jeraaṃṃan in jikin."

#: front-page.php:511
msgid "What we believe"
msgstr "Etke jej tōmak"

#: front-page.php:513
msgid "Information access is a community right"
msgstr "Maroñ bōk melele ej kien an jikin"

#: front-page.php:516
msgid "Every resident deserves to know what decisions are being made that affect their community — in language they can understand, at a time when they can still participate."
msgstr "Armej ro otemjej rej jeraaṃṃan bwe ren jeļā etke ko rej keemem ñan jikin ko aer — ilo kajin rej maroñ jeļā, ilo iien rej bōrọọriik ke wōt bōk oktak."

#: front-page.php:534
msgid "Strictly nonpartisan"
msgstr "Jab ñan jabdewōt parti"

#: front-page.php:535
msgid "Civi.Me does not endorse candidates, parties, or positions on any issue. We present facts: what a bill does, who submitted it, when the hearing is. We provide tools and templates — never talking points."
msgstr "Civi.Me ejjab kōjparok ri-kotak, parti, ak maroñ ko ilo jabdewōt ia. Jej kwaļọk tōtōin: etke bil eo ej kōṃṃan, wōn ej kaktoke, ak iien eo an roñjake. Jej leļọk kein im jikin kōjbar — jab jabdewōt iien lōmnak ko."

#: front-page.php:549
msgid "Everyone is included — no exceptions"
msgstr "Armej ro otemjej rej ilo — ejjeļọk ko im rūttōn"

#: front-page.php:550
msgid "We use \"residents\" — not \"citizens.\" We support all 15 languages recognized by Hawaii's Office of Language Access. We build for mobile and include a phone line for people who don't have a smartphone at all."
msgstr "Jej jibwi \"ri-jikin\" — jab \"ri-kien.\" Jej kōjparok kajin 15 ko otemjej rej jeļā kōn Office in Kajin an Hawaii. Jej kōṃṃan ñan mobile im ej bar ñan line in telebon ñan armej ro rejjab aikuj smartphone."

#: front-page.php:561
msgid "Cultural respect is not optional"
msgstr "Aenōṃṃan joñak ejjab kotak"

#: front-page.php:562
msgid "Native Hawaiian sovereignty is a living issue, not history. We frame civic participation as community engagement — not blind deference to government structures."
msgstr "Mour an ri-Hawaii ej ia eo emōj, jab historia. Jej kōjjeļā bōk oktak kien ej kōjparok in jikin — jab jen jab jeļā ñan kien ko."

#: front-page.php:573
msgid "Open source and community-built"
msgstr "Kōmmelele im kōṃṃan kōn jikin"

#: front-page.php:574
msgid "Civi.Me's code is public on GitHub from day one. Civic infrastructure should be open to inspection, contribution, and community ownership. If we ever make a decision you disagree with, you can see exactly why — and you can help us do better."
msgstr "Kōd an Civi.Me ej jikin ilo GitHub jen raan eo ṃōttan. Infrastrakta in kien ekwe em̧ōj kōmmelele ñan lale, kōttar, im kien an jikin. Ñe jej kōṃṃan keemem ko kwōjab melele, kwōmaroñ lale bōlen etke — im kwōmaroñ jipañ im kōṃṃan aenōṃṃan."

#: front-page.php:589
msgid "Join us"
msgstr "Itok wōt ippām̧"

#: front-page.php:591
msgid "Help build civic infrastructure for Hawaii"
msgstr "Jipañ kōṃṃan infrastrakta in kien ñan Hawaii"

#: front-page.php:594
msgid "Civi.Me is open source and community-driven. Whether you're a developer, a civic advocate, or just someone who cares — there's a place for you."
msgstr "Civi.Me ej kōmmelele im jikin ej kōṃṃane. Ñe kwōj developer, ri-kōjparok kien, ak armej eo ej kajitōk — ewōr jikin ñan eok."

